cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.HC 

This paper discusses the incorporation of cognitive theories of human creativity into generative deep learning techniques, which suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The use of convolutional neural networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the discussion of intrinsic motivation and the psychology of creativity suggests a potential overlap with human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
